{"tid":2252163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暖！正妹護理師巧手幫退休老師升旗","createTime":"2020-10-21T09:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T09:53:16.000Z","uid":105567,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c8073ee17eb93fe84997dbb55937b517dc549efc","tid":2252163,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"記者李鴻典／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n南投75歲白姓退休師因腹主動脈瘤緊急住院，經醫護悉心照料2個多月後狀況好轉，日前恰逢雙十國慶，護理師陳俞廷隨意一句「老師，今天是國慶日，您想參加升旗典禮嗎？」，患者聽了頓時精神大好頻頻點頭，於是她巧手製作國旗，再用點滴架模擬「升旗大典」，果然讓<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">老翁笑得合不攏嘴，也激起復健動力</span></strong></span>，也讓親友感動直誇「人美心也美」！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/h1l6X46v5s9hyPqeiKbElA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/setn.com.tw/1eab0ab134e1c2395e354a5325592414\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fh1l6X46v5s9hyPqeiKbElA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NTMz%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F1eab0ab134e1c2395e354a5325592414&h=ab81606d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9A%96-%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E5%B8%AB%E5%B7%A7%E6%89%8B%E5%B9%AB%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%8D%87%E6%97%97-032550640.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259A%2596-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25A6%25B9%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%25B7%25A7%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%25B9%25AB%25E9%2580%2580%25E4%25BC%2591%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E5%258D%2587%25E6%2597%2597-032550640.html&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=a91fe7ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9A%96-%E6%AD%A3%E5%A6%B9%E8%AD%B7%E7%90%86%E5%B8%AB%E5%B7%A7%E6%89%8B%E5%B9%AB%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E5%8D%87%E6%97%97-032550640.html</a>"},{"pid":"a99e3a1fa81301fef3251fec6d2ebf4edfd1585c","tid":2252163,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":